comment.body:
More and more reports of this have continued to come in with the most recent one being about DNSMadeEasy at https://github.com/certbot/certbot/issues/9818. We also have reports about this for NS1 above in this issue.

I personally found the cleaned up logs from https://github.com/certbot/certbot/issues/9818 to be particularly helpful. Why did the requested URLs change?

@adferrand, what's your schedule for doing free work on open source projects looking like for the next week or so? You're certainly more familiar with this stuff than me, but I can use some of my EFF time to start digging into this more deeply if that's at all desired.
